<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Скидання паролю</title>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Mulish:200,300,regular,500,600,700,800,900,200italic,300italic,italic,500italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,900italic"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nunito+Sans:200,300,regular,500,600,700,800,900,200italic,300italic,italic,500italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,900italic"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --back-color-1: #2C2C2C;
            --back-color-2: #9CBF4E;
            --back-color-3: #0088CC;
            --back-color-4: #dc143c;
            --back-color-5: #353535;
            --text-color-1: #FFFFFF;
            --text-color-2: #E2E2E2;
            --text-color-3: #A3A3A3;
            --text-color-4: #9CBF4E;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #222222;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template: 70px minmax(auto, 1fr) minmax(223px, 278px) / 1fr;
        }

        header {
            padding: 0 25px;
            background-color: #2C2C2C;
            width: 100%;
            height: 70px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            color: var(--text-color-1);
            font-family: Nunito Sans, sans-serif;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 125%;
        }

        .content {
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            height: 400px;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 0 23px;
            min-width: 350px;
            max-width: 450px;
            height: 340px;
            background-color: var(--back-color-1);
            border-radius: 9px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }

        .container>.container__title {
            color: var(--text-color-1);
            font-family: Nunito Sans, sans-serif;
            font-size: 23px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .container>.container__user {
            color: var(--text-color-2);
            font-family: Nunito Sans;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .container>.container__text {
            color: var(--text-color-3);
            text-align: justify;
            font-family: Mulish;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-color-1);
            font-family: Mulish;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--back-color-2);
            border-radius: 23px;
            padding: 7px 15px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 44px;
            transition: all 250ms;
        }

        .button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 19px 1px rgba(156, 191, 78, 0.2);
        }

        .button.telegram,
        .button.youtube {
            width: 176px;
            height: 42px;
            font-family: Mulish;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .button.telegram {
            background-color: var(--back-color-3);
        }

        .button.telegram:hover {
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 19px 1px rgba(0, 136, 204, 0.2);
        }

        .button.youtube {
            background-color: var(--back-color-4);
        }

        .button.youtube:hover {
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 19px 1px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.2);
        }

        .button.button__icon {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 4px;
        }

        .button.button__icon>img {
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 0 25px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .footer::before {
            content: '';
            margin: 20px 0;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--back-color-5);
        }

        .footer>.footer__row {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .footer__row>.footer__column {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .footer__subscription {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .footer__subscription>a {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }

        .footer__subtitle {
            color: var(--text-color-1);
            font-family: Mulish;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .link {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .link.link__main {
            color: var(--text-color-4);
            font-family: Mulish;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 125%;
        }

        .footer__right {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 12px;
            color: var(--text-color-1);
            font-family: Nunito Sans;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width:560px) {
            .footer>.footer__row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .footer_column {
                text-align: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">
                MovieParty
            </div>
        </header>
        <main class="content">
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="container__title">Cкидання паролю</h1>
                <h2 class="container__user">Привіт, {{name}}, ви хотіли би скинути пароль?</h2>
                <p class="container__text">Хтось (сподіваємось, ви) попросив нас скинути пароль для вашого облікового
                    запису Twitch. Для цього натисніть кнопку нижче. Якщо ви не надсилали запит на скидання пароля,
                    можете ігнорувати цей електронний лист!
                </p>
                <a class="button" href="{{link}}" target="_blank">Скинути пароль</a>
            </div>
        </main>
        <footer>
            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer__row">
                    <div class="footer_column">
                        <div class="logo">
                            MovieParty
                        </div>
                        <div class="footer__subscription">
                            <a href="https://web.telegram.org/" class="button button__icon telegram" target="_blank">
                                <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/gans-random.appspot.com/o/icons%2Ftelegram.png?alt=media&token=6262378d-0f58-41d6-835d-ef824106c0cb"
                                    alt="Telegram">
                                Telegram
                            </a>
                            <a href="https://youtube.com/" class="button button__icon youtube" target="_blank">
                                <img src="https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/gans-random.appspot.com/o/icons%2Fyoutube.png?alt=media&token=03a2c7b8-d296-4eb1-9c74-63ae2cf86ffb"
                                    alt="YouTube">
                                YouTube
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer_column">
                        <div class="footer__subtitle">
                            Контакти
                        </div>
                        <a href="#" class="link link__main">movieparty.team@gmail.com</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer__right">
                    2024 All right reserved
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>